\sum_{1\leq i,j \leq n} \langle c_i ,c_j \rangle \times  \langle l_i ,l_j \rangle \leq \left( \sum_{i=1}^n||c_i||^2 \right)\left( \sum_{i=1}^n||l_i||^2 \right)
\sum_{1\leq i \neq j \leq n} \langle c_i ,c_j \rangle \times  \langle l_i ,l_j \rangle \leq  \sum_{1\leq i\neq j\leq n} ||c_i||^2 ||l_i||^2 
