\sum_{1\leqslant i,j\leqslant n}\langle c_i,c_j\rangle\cdot\langle l_i,l_j\rangle\leqslant\left(\sum_{i=1}^n\lVert c_i\rVert\cdot \lVert l_i\rVert\right)^2.
